b'Soukou Kihei Votoms: Kakuyaku taru Ita: b'Chirico is awoken from cold sleep and separated from Fyana. His attempts to find her come to the attention of a Nextant, the replacement for the Perfect Soldier program. At the same time, the new Pope is to be nominated, and Chirico is religiously considered to be "The Untouchable". With one of the nominees related to the Nextant, Chirico\'s actions will have far-reaching political ramifications.\n\n(Source: ANN)'
